      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software development lifecycle documentation, version control, and regression testing must meet MRL 5 requirements for Class III device submission.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation is incomplete; version control is present but regression test suite covers only 40% of solver modules. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and manufactured solution benchmarks must confirm solver implementation correctness for hemolysis transport equations.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed for Navier-Stokes but not for the power-law hemolysis transport scalar. Partial verification only; achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
