      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent grid convergence study must quantify discretization error contribution to hemolysis index predictions.",
      "rationale": "Three-level grid convergence study was performed; GCI values for hemolysis index range 8–22% depending on operating point, exceeding acceptable thresholds for MRL 5. Achieved level 2."
