      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Hemolysis index QoI must be directly linked to clinical endpoint (plasma-free hemoglobin) with traceability to the clinical acceptance threshold.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is directly mapped to normalized index of hemolysis (NIH); clinical threshold traceability is established but sensitivity of NIH to model parameter uncertainty is not fully quantified. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
