      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under blood-analog conditions spanning the full VAD operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation used water-glycerol analog rather than porcine blood; geometric fidelity is high but fluid rheology mismatch introduces unquantified extrapolation uncertainty. Achieved level 2."
    },
