      "acceptanceCriteria": "Uncertainty in the power-law hemolysis damage model form must be quantified relative to alternative hemolysis model formulations (e.g., strain-based, energy dissipation-based).",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was employed; no model-form uncertainty quantification against alternative formulations was performed. Critical gap at MRL 5; not assessed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
