      "acceptanceCriteria": "Probability distributions for hemolysis model coefficients (C, alpha, beta) and blood rheology parameters must be characterized and propagated via Monte Carlo UQ.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input distributions for hemolysis model coefficients were taken from literature without uncertainty characterization of the coefficient estimation process itself. Not assessed."
