      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between CFD boundary conditions and experimental inlet/outlet conditions must be formally demonstrated including flow profile specification.",
      "rationale": "Uniform velocity inlet profiles were assumed in CFD; experimental inlet flow conditioning was not characterized. Equivalency of inlet turbulence intensity is unverified. Not assessed."
